sequenceDiagram
    participant ML as ML Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Online as Online Feature Server<br/>6566/6567 HTTP/gRPC
    participant Registry as Registry Server<br/>6570/6571 gRPC TLS1.2+
    participant Store as Redis/PostgreSQL/SQLite<br/>6379/5432 TLS1.2+
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over ML,OIDC: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)

    ML->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>OIDC: Validate JWT Token
    OIDC-->>Route: Token Valid
    Route->>Online: Forward Request<br/>gRPC/HTTP TLS1.2+
    Online->>OIDC: Validate Bearer Token
    OIDC-->>Online: Token Valid
    Online->>Registry: Get Feature Metadata<br/>gRPC 6570/6571
    Registry-->>Online: Feature View Schema
    Online->>Store: Query Features<br/>Redis/PostgreSQL Protocol
    Store-->>Online: Feature Values
    Online-->>Route: JSON Response
    Route-->>ML: Feature Data

    Note over ML,OIDC: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Training)

    participant Train as Training Job
    participant Offline as Offline Feature Server<br/>8815/8816 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Train->>Route: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Offline: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Offline->>OIDC: Validate Bearer Token
    OIDC-->>Offline: Token Valid
    Offline->>Registry: Get Feature Metadata<br/>gRPC 6570/6571
    Registry-->>Offline: Feature View Schema
    Offline->>S3: Fetch Offline Data<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Offline: Historical Features
    Offline-->>Route: JSON Response
    Route-->>Train: Historical Feature Data

    Note over ML,OIDC: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)

    participant Cron as CronJob<br/>Scheduled Task

    Cron->>Online: POST /materialize<br/>Bearer/mTLS
    Online->>Offline: GET /get-historical-features<br/>HTTPS 8816
    Offline->>S3: Fetch Latest Features<br/>AWS IAM
    S3-->>Offline: Feature Data
    Offline-->>Online: Feature Batch
    Online->>Store: Write Features<br/>Redis/PostgreSQL
    Store-->>Online: Write Confirmed
    Online-->>Cron: Materialization Complete

    Note over ML,OIDC: Flow 4: Feature Registry Management

    participant CLI as feast CLI / SDK
    participant RegREST as Registry Server REST<br/>6572/6573 HTTP/HTTPS

    CLI->>RegREST: POST /registry<br/>Apply FeatureView<br/>Bearer Token
    RegREST->>OIDC: Validate Token
    OIDC-->>RegREST: Token Valid
    RegREST->>Store: Persist Metadata<br/>PostgreSQL/S3
    Store-->>RegREST: Write Confirmed
    RegREST-->>CLI: FeatureView Applied

    Note over ML,OIDC: Flow 5: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Op as Feast Operator
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3

    Op->>K8s: Watch FeatureStore CR<br/>Service Account Token
    K8s-->>Op: CR Created/Updated
    Op->>K8s: Create Deployments<br/>Online/Offline/Registry
    Op->>K8s: Create Services
    Op->>K8s: Create ConfigMaps
    Op->>K8s: Create OpenShift Routes
    K8s-->>Op: Resources Created
    Op->>K8s: Update CR Status
